<topic id="configuration">
    <title>Configuration</title>
    <shortdesc>Configure the project using Gradle properties.</shortdesc>
    <body>
        <section>
            <title>Gradle Properties</title>
            <p>The following properties can be set on the command line or in
               <codeph>gradle.properties</codeph>:</p>
            <table>
                <tgroup cols="3">
                    <colspec colname="c1"/>
                    <colspec colname="c2"/>
                    <colspec colname="c3"/>
                    <thead>
                        <row>
                            <entry>Property</entry>
                            <entry>Default</entry>
                            <entry>Description</entry>
                        </row>
                    </thead>
                    <tbody>
                        <row>
                            <entry><codeph>ditaOtVersion</codeph></entry>
                            <entry>4.2.3</entry>
                            <entry>DITA-OT version to download</entry>
                        </row>
                        <row>
                            <entry><codeph>pluginId</codeph></entry>
                            <entry>org.lwdita</entry>
                            <entry>Plugin ID to install from registry</entry>
                        </row>
                        <row>
                            <entry><codeph>transtype</codeph></entry>
                            <entry>markdown</entry>
                            <entry>Transformation type to run</entry>
                        </row>
                    </tbody>
                </tgroup>
            </table>
        </section>

        <section>
            <title>Example Configurations</title>
            <p>Test with different DITA-OT versions:</p>
            <codeblock>./gradlew -PditaOtVersion=4.0.0 test
./gradlew -PditaOtVersion=4.1.0 test
./gradlew -PditaOtVersion=4.2.3 test</codeblock>

            <p>Test different plugins:</p>
            <codeblock>./gradlew -PpluginId=org.lwdita -Ptranstype=markdown test
./gradlew -PpluginId=org.dita.normalize test</codeblock>
        </section>
    </body>
</topic>
